Decompose the task into a maximum of 2 focused subproblems. If the task requires more sub-tasks than available helpers, you must group related sub-tasks together within a single helper's instructions. For each helper, you must explicitly include the relevant portion of the input data within their instructions so they can perform their analysis. The synthesis brief must explain how to combine these grouped results into the final required format.

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}
